The setlist too. I'm doing so many things I wanted to do.

403
00:30:52,593 --> 00:30:54,693
まだやれてないことあるんじゃないですか？
Isn't there still something you haven't done yet?

404
00:30:54,693 --> 00:30:56,193
あります！
There is!

405
00:30:56,193 --> 00:30:57,493
というわけで！
And so!

406
00:30:57,493 --> 00:30:58,293
ということで！
That means!

407
00:30:58,293 --> 00:31:00,693
二人来てよー！すいちゃん、わためぇ！
Come on out, you two! Sui-chan, Watame!

